Package: mcmapper
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohsen", "Sadatsafavi", , "mohsen.sadatsafavi@ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0419-7862"))
Description: The goal of mcmapper is to enable estimating the parameters of two-parameter distributions for risks (e.g., beta, logit-normal) based on the expected value and c-statistic of the distribution. The theory behind this approach is explained in Sadatsafavi et al..
